sec.p:
Hourly PV production and weather data (temperature, humidity and solar irradiance) from 7 PV plants are exploited. PV production data are collected directly from the solar plant systems of a Portuguese energy community, while weather data are extracted from a local meteorological station34 and the Copernicus Atmosphere Data Store35. One PV plant, namely PV1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
